Package: ghostty
Architecture: amd64
Description: A fast, feature-rich, and cross-platform terminal emulator.
 Ghostty is a fast, feature-rich, and cross-platform terminal emulator that
 uses platform-native UI and GPU acceleration. It is developed by Mitchell
 Hashimoto and packaged for Ubuntu by the community.
